Thank you to all #givingtuesday donors! You help us to continue to provide inquiry-based learning experiences.

As part of their Energy unit of inquiry, 4th graders heard from guest speakers Cheri Harrington (COO, Yu Ying) and
@DCInternationalSchool COO, Denise Lyons, regarding Yu Ying and DCI's energy saving mechanisms. This week, 4th graders are designing their own energy-efficient school blueprint!

A reminder that Yu Ying is taking over @charteralliance Instagram TOMORROW - Tuesday, May 14th! Be sure to tune in to see a day in the life at Yu Ying. https://www.instagram.com/charteralliance/?hl=en

